    "BERT had the lowest performance among the models but still demonstrated solid NER capabilities.",
    "Overall, DeBERTa and BioBERT showed the best performance in this task.",
    "The analysis of the KSR task results shows that DeBERTa and BioBERT outperformed the other models, achieving the highest scores across all metrics.",
